---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Terms of Service"
  description="YardFavorites Terms of Service - your rights and our obligations."
>
  <section class="py-12">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 prose prose-lg">
      <h1>Terms of Service</h1>
      <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> March 2025</p>
      <h2>Acceptance of Terms</h2>
      <p>
        By using YardFavorites, you agree to these terms. If you do not agree,
        please do not use this site.
      </p>
      <h2>Content Accuracy</h2>
      <p>
        Our reviews and guides represent our honest opinions based on real-world testing.
        We strive for accuracy but cannot guarantee that all information is current or complete.
      </p>
      <h2>Affiliate Links</h2>
      <p>
        YardFavorites is a participant in the Amazon Associates Program.
        We earn commissions from qualifying purchases made through links on this site,
        at no additional cost to you.
      </p>
      <h2>Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p>
        YardFavorites is not responsible for any purchase decisions made based on
        our content. Always do your own research before buying.
      </p>
      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>Questions? Email <strong>hello@yardfavorites.com</strong></p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
